u do not have permission to restore roles.'=>'您没有权限恢复角色。','You do not have permission to perform this action.'=>'您没有权限执行此操作。','If you like %s, please leave us a %s rating. Thank you!'=>'如果您喜欢 %s，请给我们留下 %s 评分。谢谢！','About PublishPress Capabilities'=>'关于 PublishPress 能力','About'=>'关于','Capabilites Documentation'=>'能力文档','Documentation'=>'文档','Contact the PublishPress team'=>'联系 PublishPress 团队','Contact'=>'联系','Permissions & Access'=>'权限与访问','Administer advanced content permissions and visibility rules.'=>'管理高级内容权限和可见性规则。','Manage plugin permission settings.'=>'管理插件权限设置。','Bypass content restrictions for editorial workflows.'=>'绕过内容限制以进行编辑工作流程。','Set custom post statuses for content items.'=>'为内容项设置自定义帖子状态。','Force Quick Edit access when restrictions would otherwise block it.'=>'在限制会阻止访问时强制快速编辑访问。','Roles & Groups'=>'角色与组','Assign or change role assignments for users.'=>'为用户分配或更改角色分配。','Create new permission groups.'=>'创建新的权限组。','Edit existing permission groups.'=>'编辑现有的权限组。','Delete permission groups.'=>'删除权限组。','Add or remove members from permission groups.'=>'从权限组中添加或移除成员。','Create network-wide permission groups in multisite.'=>'在多站点中创建网络范围的权限组。','Manage members of network-wide permission groups.'=>'管理网络范围的权限组成员。','Exception Management'=>'异常管理','Set per-item association exceptions.'=>'设置每项关联的异常。','Set per-item edit exceptions.'=>'设置每项编辑的异常。','Set per-item read exceptions.'=>'设置每项读取的异常。','Set per-item revision exceptions.'=>'设置每项修订的异常。','Set taxonomy term assignment exceptions.'=>'设置分类术语分配的异常。','Set taxonomy term association exceptions.'=>'设置分类术语关联的异常。','Set taxonomy term management exceptions.'=>'设置分类术语管理的异常。','Content Associations'=>'内容关联','Associate users or groups with any page.'=>'将用户或组与任何页面关联。','Define and apply custom post statuses.'=>'定义并应用自定义帖子状态。','Define custom privacy policies for content.'=>'为内容定义自定义隐私政策。','Moderate any item regardless of authorship.'=>'对任何项目进行审核，无论作者身份如何。','Media & Misc'=>'媒体与杂项','Edit attachments uploaded by the current user.'=>'编辑当前用户上传的附件。','List unattached files uploaded by other users.'=>'列出其他用户上传的未附加文件。','List all media library files.'=>'列出所有媒体库文件。','Exempt user from edit-circle restrictions.'=>'免除用户的编辑圈限制。','Exempt user from read-circle restrictions.'=>'免除用户的阅读圈限制。','see %1$sRole Usage%2$s: "Pattern Roles"'=>'查看 %1$s角色使用情况%2$s：“模式角色”','activate %1$sAdvanced settings%2$s, see Role Usage'=>'激活 %1$s高级设置%2$s，查看角色使用情况','"Posts" capabilities selected here also define type-specific role assignment for Permission Groups%s.'=>'"帖子"的能力在此处选择，也定义了权限组%s的特定类型角色分配。','"Posts" capabilities selected here also define type-specific role assignment for Permit Groups%s.'=>'"帖子"的能力在此处选择，也定义了许可组%s的特定类型角色分配。','Capabilities for custom statuses can be manually added here. (See %sPermissions > Post Statuses%s for applicable names). %sSupplemental status-specific roles%s are usually more convenient, though.'=>'可以在此手动添加自定义状态的能力。（请参见%s权限 > 帖子状态%s以获取适用名称）。%s补充状态特定角色%s通常更方便。','Capabilities for custom statuses can be manually added here. Or activate the PP Custom Post Statuses extension to assign status-specific supplemental roles.'=>'可以在此手动添加自定义状态的能力。或激活PP自定义帖子状态扩展以分配状态特定的补充角色。','Capabilities for custom statuses can be manually added to a role here (see Conditions > Status > Capability Mapping for applicable names). However, it is usually more convenient to use Permit Groups to assign a supplemental status-specific role.'=>'可以在此向角色手动添加自定义状态的能力（请参见条件 > 状态 > 能力映射以获取适用名称）。不过，通常使用许可组来分配一个补充状态特定角色更方便。','Unique Post Type Capabilities'=>'唯一的帖子类型功能','Allow post type permissions to be controlled separately from other areas of WordPress. %1$sFind out more.%2$s'=>'允许单独控制帖子类型权限与WordPress的其他区域。%1$s了解更多信息。%2$s','Use the "Create" capability for selected post types'=>'为选定的帖子类型使用“创建”功能','This will cause a new capability to be required for creating posts, and enable a checkbox column here for role assignments. Normally, post creation is controlled by the "Edit" capability.'=>'这将导致创建帖子需要新的能力，并在此处启用一个复选框列以进行角色分配。通常，帖子创建由"编辑"能力控制。','Update'=>'更新','Unique Taxonomy Capabilities'=>'唯一的分类法功能','Allow taxonomy permissions to be controlled separately from other areas of WordPress.'=>'允许单独控制分类权限与WordPress的其他区域。','Detailed Taxonomy Capabilities'=>'详细的分类能力','Allow "Edit", "Delete" and "Assign" capabilities separately from the "Manage" capability.'=>'允许单独控制"编辑"、"删除"和"分配"能力与"管理"能力。','Login Redirect'=>'登录重定向','Logout Redirect'=>'注销重定向','Registration Redirect'=>'注册重定向','First Login Redirect'=>'首次登录重定向','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after login.'=>'输入此角色用户登录后应重定向到的URL。','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after logout.'=>'输入此角色用户注销后应重定向到的URL。','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after registration.'=>'输入此角色用户注册后应重定向到的URL。','Enter the URL users in this role should be redirected to after their first login.'=>'输入此角色在第一次登录后应重定向的URL。','%s Redirects'=>'%s 重定向','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','Redirect users to the URL they were viewing before login.'=>'将用户重定向到他们登录前查看的URL。','Redirect users to a specified URL.'=>'将用户重定向到指定的URL。','Enter the relative path only without domain for login redirect.'=>'仅输入相对路径，不带域名用于登录重定向。','You must enter the Login Redirect URL.'=>'您必须输入登录重定向URL。','Enter the relative path only without domain for logout redirect.'=>'仅输入相对路径，不带域名用于注销重定向。','Redirect Features allows you to redirect users in a role after Registration, Login or Logout.'=>'重定向功能允许您在注册、登录或注销后重定向用户角色。','How to use Redirect Features'=>'如何使用重定向功能','You do not have sufficient permissions to perform this action.'=>'您没有足够的权限来执行此操作。','Your link has expired, refresh the page and try again.'=>'您的链接已过期，请刷新页面并重试。','Missing parameters, refresh the page and try again.'=>'缺少参数，请刷新页面并重试。','Invalid role name entry: %s'=>'无效的角色名称输入：%s','The role "%s" already exists. Please choose a different name.'=>'角色 "%s" 已存在。请选一个不同的名称。','Something went wrong, the system wasn\'t able to create the role, refresh the page and try again.'=>'出了点问题，系统无法创建角色，请刷新页面并重试。','The new role %s was created successfully.'=>'新角色 %s 创建成功。','%s role updated successfully.'=>'%s 角色更新成功。','Cannot delete default role. You <a href="%s">have to change it first</a>.'=>'无法删除默认角色。您 <a href="%s">必须先更改它</a>。','Deleting a system role is not allowed.'=>'不允许删除系统角色。','%1$d users moved to default role %2$s.'=>'%1$d 用户已移动到默认角色 %2$s。','The role %1$s was successfully deleted. %2$s'=>'角色 %1$s 已成功删除。 %2$s','The selected %1$s roles were successfully deleted. %2$s'=>'选定的 %1$s 角色已成功删除。 %2$s','The role could not be deleted.'=>'角色无法删除。','The role %1$s was successfully hidden.'=>'角色 %1$s 已成功隐藏。','The role %1$s was successfully unhidden.'=>'角色 %1$s 已成功取消隐藏。','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','Gutenberg editor'=>'古腾堡编辑器','Classic editor'=>'经典编辑器','Role Slug'=>'角色别名','The "slug" is the URL-friendly version of the role. It is usually all lowercase and contains only letters, numbers and underscores.'=>'"slug"是角色的URL友好版本。它通常全部为小写，仅包含字母、数字和下划线。','Block Login'=>'阻止登录','Block users in this role from logging into the site.'=>'阻止该角色的用户登录网站。','Block Dashboard Access'=>'阻止仪表盘访问','Block users in this role from accessing admin area.'=>'阻止该角色的用户访问管理区域。','Role Level'=>'角色级别','Each user role has a level from 0 to 10. The Subscriber role defaults to the lowest level (0). The Administrator role defaults to level 10.'=>'每个用户角色的级别从0到10。订阅者角色默认为最低级别（0）。管理员角色默认为级别10。','Delete role'=>'删除角色','Deleting this role will completely remove it from database and is irrecoverable.'=>'删除此角色将完全从数据库中移除，并且无法恢复。','Disable Code Editor'=>'禁用代码编辑器','Disable the "Code editor" option for the Gutenberg block editor.'=>'为 Gutenberg 块编辑器禁用 "代码编辑器" 选项。','Control Allowed Editors'=>'控制允许的编辑器','Select the allowed editor options for users in this role.'=>'为该角色的用户选择允许的编辑器选项。','Disable WooCommerce admin restrictions'=>'禁用 WooCommerce 管理限制','By default, WooCommerce prevents most users from accessing the WordPress admin area. When enabled, this setting will remove those restrictions for this role. %1s Click here for more details. %2s'=>'默认情况下，WooCommerce阻止大多数用户访问WordPress管理员区域。当启用时，此设置将移除该角色的这些限制。%1s 点击此处了解更多详情。%2s','Slug already exists'=>'别名已存在','Select allowed editor'=>'选择允许的编辑器','You must select at least one editor for the role when managing allowed editor.'=>'管理允许的编辑器时，您必须为角色选择至少一个编辑器。','Select %s'=>'选择 %s','Read more on Role Level.'=>'阅读更多关于角色级别的信息。','Are you sure you want to delete this role?'=>'您确定要删除此角色吗？','%s role copied. Please click the "Create Role" button to create this new role.'=>'%s 角色已复制。请点击“创建角色”按钮以创建此新角色。','Edit Role: %s'=>'编辑角色：%s','Copy Role'=>'复制角色','Create New Role'=>'创建新角色','All Roles'=>'所有角色','These can be edited on the %1s Capabilities screen %2s'=>'这些可以在 %1s 权限屏幕 %2s 上进行编辑','Load More'=>'加载更多','Load Less'=>'加载更少','All %s'=>'所有 %s','Mine %s'=>'我的 %s','Has Users %s'=>'有用户 %s','No Users %s'=>'没有用户 %s','Editable %s'=>'可编辑 %s','Uneditable %s'=>'不可编辑 %s','System %s'=>'系统 %s','Copy'=>'复制','(non-editable role)'=>'(不可编辑角色)','Unhide'=>'取消隐藏','Your Role'=>'您的角色','WordPress Core'=>'WordPress 核心','Search Roles'=>'搜索角色','Multiples roles on "Add New User" screen'=>'在 "添加新用户" 屏幕上选择多个角色','This allows you to assign a new user to multiples roles.'=>'这允许您将新用户分配给多个角色。','Multiples roles on "User Edit" screen'=>'在 "用户编辑" 屏幕上选择多个角色','This allows you to assign an existing user to multiple roles.'=>'这允许您将现有用户分配给多个角色。','Set login redirect cookie'=>'设置登录重定向 cookie','Use cookie to determine pages users were viewing before login. This is useful when login redirect is not working correctly due to wp_get_referer() limitation.'=>'使用 cookie 确定用户在登录之前查看的页面。当由于 wp_get_referer() 的限制而导致登录重定向无法正常工作时，这非常有用。','Show private post types'=>'显示私有帖子类型','This will show all post types on the "Capabilities" screen, even ones normally hidden in the WordPress admin area.'=>'这将在“能力”屏幕上显示所有帖子类型，即使是通常在 WordPress 管理区域中隐藏的帖子类型。','Show private taxonomies'=>'显示私有分类法','This will show all taxonomies on the "Capabilities" screen, even ones normally hidden in the WordPress admin area.'=>'这将在“能力”屏幕上显示所有分类法，即使是通常在 WordPress 管理区域中隐藏的分类法。','Show all post types on the "Editor Features" screen, even ones normally hidden in the WordPress admin area.'=>'在“编辑器功能”屏幕上显示所有帖子类型，即使是通常在 WordPress 管理区域中隐藏的帖子类型。','Enable Classic Editor tab'=>'启用经典编辑器标签','Always show the Classic Editor tab in "Editor Features" screen.'=>'始终在 "编辑器功能" 屏幕上显示经典编辑器标签。','Admin Bar modification'=>'管理栏修改','When testing, display a caption and return link in the Admin Bar.'=>'在测试时，在管理栏中显示标题和返回链接。','Admin Bar search'=>'管理栏搜索','Add option to search and user testing in the Admin Bar.'=>'在管理栏中添加搜索和用户测试的选项。','Front End footer notice'=>'前端页脚通知','When testing, display a return link in the front end footer.'=>'在测试时，在前端页脚中显示返回链接。','Exclude role from User Testing'=>'从用户测试中排除角色','Select roles...'=>'选择角色...','Exclude users in selected roles from User Testing.'=>'从用户测试中排除选定角色的用户。','Automatically refresh profile elements'=>'自动刷新配置文件元素','Always try to automatically find profile elements. This may cause temporary issues when updating user roles that do not have access to the WordPress admin area.'=>'始终尝试自动查找配置文件元素。当更新没有访问 WordPress 管理区域的用户角色时，这可能会导致临时问题。','Capabilities Settings'=>'能力设置','Search user...'=>'搜索用户...','Search'=>'搜索','No results found.'=>'未找到结果。','Permission denied.'=>'权限被拒绝。','Test user'=>'测试用户','Test this user'=>'测试此用户','Testing: '=>'测试中： ','%1$sReturn to Administrator view%2$s'=>'%1$s返回管理员视图%2$s','Testing as user: %1$s. %2$sReturn to Administrator view%3$s'=>'以用户身份测试：%1$s。 %2$s返回管理员视图%3$s','Unable to retrieve user data.'=>'无法检索用户数据。']];